name: Icons set for the Web
description:
A usual set of icons for the WEB

It's outlines icons with a line thickness of 1.5 px. Icons with rounded corners and endings path. Roundings of 0.25, 0.5, 1 and 2 pixels are used, no sharp corners. The icon's frame is to 24/24 pixels.

  • Navigations - basic navigation icons in the interface
  • Actions - icons of actions, start, change or end an action
  • Entity - icons of entities, showing events, phenomena or subjects
  • Info - information icons, shows status/action/progress

The card shows an example of using my icons. 

Goodluck, enjoy this set and check my Dribbble here ->
